Getit,Hot,Deals,is,a,website,designed,to,help,businesses,and,customers,in,more,than,cities,in,India,connect,with,each,other,Local,businesses,can,advertise,their,products,and,sales,through,the,site,and,prospective,customers,can,use,the,site,to,search,for,the,products,and,services,that,they,need,The,Getit,Hot,Deals,API,enables,users,to,interact,with,the,site,programmatically,Some,uses,include,searching,the,site,and,retrieving,cached,Hot,Deals,The,API,can,be,accessed,using,SOAP,calls,issued,in,XML,format